    "type": "message",
    "text": "There’s immense potential for an individual to derive immense value for themselves by creating unique prompts on the fly. I “prompted” a LugoOS that was able to pair code with me, while asking probing questions along the way as I specified to “check in” with my mental state because I was having a bad day. I mean I have to choose to read it and interpret it, but that’s something a fraction of a fraction of people in the world could even think to have access to. It’s been driving motivation for me again. \n",
